webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) Einar Ahlström’s speceri and diversebusiness in Väsby, Oppeby. The building was built around 1850 and, at the time of the picture, housed an apartment about a room and a kitchen with a business and post office in the ground floor. The single cottage on the left is of older date, traveled in the early 1700s. In the background, Oppeby’s church is glimpsed - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMFB000542. AB Flygtrafik. Östergötlands museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021016419858. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
